Kevin and Sophia Martin

Did the hardwork so their children did not have to

Young Sophia and Kevin before they entered parenthood.

  • 1971 - Kevin was born in Portmore, Jamaica.

  • 1974 - Sophia was born in Kingston, Jamaica.

  • 1986 - Around this time both Kevin and Sophia had immigrated to New York City, USA. They would later cross paths in their early adulthood years.

  • 2001 - Kevin and Sophia welcomed their first child (daughter) into the world.

  • 2003 - Kevin and Sophia welcomed their second child(son) into the world.

  • 2004 - Around this time, Kevin and Sophia moved to Maryland, USA to provide a better enviorment for their children. Later they acheived full citizenship in the USA.

  • 2015 - Both Kevin and Sophia earned their Bachelor of Science Degree.

  • 2019 - Sophia earned her Master's Degree. Kevin and Sophia put their first child into college.

  • 2022 - Kevin and Sophia bought their first house as well as put their second child into college.

"It's not about how you start but how you finish."

-- Kevin Martin
